Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:26.35,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}dakishimete odoru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.33,0:22:58.43,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:04.80,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, je možné, že ma dokážeš vidieť?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:08.85,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty ma vlastne poznáš?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:10.97,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš, Yuuko-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:11.96,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,To som ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:16.00,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Je možné, že sme sa už niekedy stretli?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:18.26,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:20.66,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:25.35,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi som na teba zabudla.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:28.38,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:34.22,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto si?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:35.06,ktos,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(519,413)}Kto... si?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:38.09,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Dážď zmýva spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:41.20,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Duša sa ponára do zabudnutia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.68,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,Utápa sa pokojom...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:45.57,TOA07,,0000,0000,0000,,... láska bez odozvy.
